.TH "cgroup_update_dfl_csses" 9 "cgroup_update_dfl_csses" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
cgroup_update_dfl_csses \- update css assoc of a subtree in default hierarchy
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" cgroup_update_dfl_csses
.BI "(struct cgroup *cgrp "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cgrp" 12
root of the subtree to update csses for
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
\fIcgrp\fP's control masks have changed and its subtree's css associations
need to be updated accordingly.  This function looks up all css_sets
which are attached to the subtree, creates the matching updated css_sets
and migrates the tasks to the new ones.
